CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right...Christine Bundridge, Hilly [sic] City Auxiliary sponsored...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Christine Bundridge wearing pleated plaid skirt and dark short sleeved sweater with light colored buttons and angora bib line, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
